social_posts.post_text: Ain't fuck with me back then but when she see me she say hello….

You taught me the true meaning of what Faith in the Lord truly looked like,I thank you for every prayer you said for me, and I will cherish every conversation we had. You never missed a birthday call, the first to call every single time. All I want to hear is “Hey Mamoo “ one time but I know your in heaven saying it to God 😂. Take your rest Mamoo, I love you forever 💜
I’m chillin but my swag on full attack…

There’s not enough words in this world to describe the way I feel about you baby girl. You are so smart, full of life, funny, and baby you know you can run. You teach me everyday of what it means to live life. I pray continuous blessings, favor, and growth over you my love. I’m honored to call myself your DaDa, I love you more than anything. Happy 2nd Birthday Mia Grace 🎉🥳😘…
Everybody get a shot but I’m a different Caliber…..

Happy 1st Birthday to my baby boy who has a smile that can make the sun rise in the morning. Son you are truly a blessing, it’s never a second you’re not smiling or having a good time. I pray that you continue to have that positive and energetic spirit because it’s heaven sent. You will do great things in life, remember you’re the Head and not the tail above and not beneath. DaDa loves you to the moon and back. Happy Birthday Jordan Michael Mills Jr. 🎉 🎉🎉🎂🎂
Greatest blessing God has giving me is the honor to be your DaDa❤️
